You cannot resist the all-seeing Eye of Kabala and neither shall the buxom buccaneer and her swaggering crew of corsairs! As the SheBuccaneer continues her hunt for the foundation stones of the seven seas, she finds herself consigned to the harem of a greedy Persian sultan, pursued by the monstrous warship Allah's Wind and finally face to face with a fire-breathing Jinn! Plus, get another enticing photographic centerfold and a chance to join the crew. Yo, ho, ho!
name: The Eye of Kabala

description: Having battled the devil in the Tombs of Eden, the bawdy buccaneer sets sail in search of the mythic foundation stones of the Seven Seas. She and her swarthy pirate crew voyage to the shattered shores of once great Atlantis. To survive, they must avoid being boiled alive by giant mutant cannibals and crushed by a steam-punk colossus driven by the lunatic castaway, Crazy Larry! Every page is a feast of pirate fun for the eyes and unexpected adventures to satisfy the imagination. Featuring a photo centerfold of The SheBuccaneer, plus a chance to join the crew and be in a comic book!
name: The Eye of Atlantis

description: Her beauty is matched only by the savagery of her cutlass. The She-Buccaneer, along with the crew of the pirate ship Queen's Vengeance, searches the sea for the seven gems that will open the ancient gates of Eden and free her beloved Calico Jack Rackham from the devil's grasp. On her voyages she will battle dragons, cannibalistic giants, evil genies, lusty sultans and all the mythic beasts of the deep dark sea.
name: Tombs of Eden

description:
Variant: American Entertainment version - see pic below. 
 
Synopsis :

Jerusalem, 1997.

Christie Blaze has infiltrated a secret installation and Cardinal Lazrarus is being debriefed about it. She stole the Creation Equation and made sure Lazarus and his crew knew she was an International Operations  agent. Furious with this news, Lazarus tells his second in command, Jesthra to release The Rath so they can track down Blaze.

Avignon, Southern France.

A secret order discusses the theft of the Creation Equation. They decide to call upon The Fallen , a trio of warriors tasked to retrieve the equation.

Epilogue

San Diego.

Max Faraday awakens from strange dreams. His sister Jenny tells him to hurry and get ready for work. Max tells her good things are about to happen, he's sure of it.
name: First Drafts

volume.name: Divine Right: The Adventures of Max Faraday

description: In this issue Catwoman agrees to help Batman take down a new criminal in Gotham who goes by the name of Mr. Handsome. Mr. Handsomes method of operations is to steal beautiful things and destroy them. Unfortunately for Catwoman, she is on his list.
name: Catwoman Defiant

description: Meet Blonde Phantom – she’s gorgeous, quick-witted, and hard-boiled. There was never a case that wasn’t open-and-shut for this gun-toting, two-fisted knockout of a P.I. But has she still got what it takes to bust a mystery wide open in the modern Marvel Universe? Marc Guggenheim and Javier Pulido turn the classic Blonde Phantom into Marvel’s newest hero! AND MORE! Writer/artist Michael Kupperman (Tales Designed to Thrizzle) takes on Marvex, the Super-Robot, in a hilarious bonus special feature!!
name: Murder On Another Planet

description:
Beast Boy and Flamebird roll into town on a "secret mission," but it doesn't take much counter intelligence to realize that Beast Boy wants the kids to come back to California with him so he can exert full leadership control of the next version of Titans West. Meanwhile, Jesse's mom's new fiancé is unexpectedly found dead in bed. Any idea who killed him?

Jesse Quick and the Titans uncover a shady alliance that her mom, LIberty Belle, had become involved in.
name: Friends and Lovers

description:
In the middle of the desert, the former Titan named Damage calls out for the assistance of the Titans-and Jesse Quick comes to the rescue. But are the strange voices in the desert that are haunting Damage merely ghosts'or something much more dangerous?

The Titans try to take some time off out in the desert, but as usual, trouble finds them. This time in the form of personal ghosts visiting Damage and Jesse Quick.
name: Ghost Dance Part 1

description:
Case of the Crabbes - part 1 of 2
The World's Zaniest Uncouth Sleuth!
name: Case of the Crabbes, Part 1

description: The legendary video game superstar kicks off Dreamwave's all-new Capcom line just in time for his highly touted fifteenth anniversary! When that malicious mastermind Dr. Wily threatens to conquer the world with his legions of Automatons only Dr. Light's greatest creation, the mighty super robot Mega Man can put a stop to him! The latest edition to this year's 15th anniversary celebration, that includes an animated series, toy lines and a slew of new videogames, this action-packed series promises thrills, chills and excitement for fans of all ages! Features two different covers, by series artist Mic Fong and Skottie young, shipped in a 50/50 ratio
"Skells" Myra hovers between life and death...and the Question also finds himself in a life-and-death situation!
name: Skells

description: "Almanacco Topolino" #14 and "Topolino" #184 used the same cover.
Priorities are decided and Myra, Vic and Hub City must come to terms with the future...while someone is masquerading as the Question. Guest-starring Richard Dragon.
name: Let Nothing You Dismay...

description: Continuing the re-presentation of the classic miniseries: Blood falls in love with a vampire woman and together they leave the clan of blood drinkers on a search for truth. But the thirst for blood is still part of him, and soon he will have to kill again as he struggles to come to terms with his life as a vampire.
name: Communion

description: Blood lives out a human lifetime--one replete with mortal agonies and ecstasies. But his return to a vampiric existence is tainted with tragedy as a longtime companion dies, leading Blood to the final leg of his quest.
name: Theophany

description: Concluding the re-presentation of the classic miniseries: The Woman tells Blood about her affair with the now deceased Little One while Blood was away in the modern world. Blood and The Woman continue their pursuit of the ship until The Woman dies in childbirth. Overcome with grief, Blood ages rapidly and joins a sacred pack of prophets on a journey to find the meaning of existence.
name: Uroborous
